flowchart TD
    Start([GitHub Action Triggered]) --> CheckConditions

    subgraph Step 1: Check conditions
        CheckConditions{Event Type}
        CheckConditions -->|workflow_dispatch / workflow_call| SetDefault[run=true<br/>agent=cogni-ai-architect]
        CheckConditions -->|issues / issue_comment / discussion / discussion_comment / pull_request_review_comment| CommentCheck{Check Role & Mentions}
        CheckConditions -->|pull_request / pull_request_target| PRCheck{Check Role}

        CommentCheck -->|Matches REVIEW_TRIGGERS| SetReviewer[run=true<br/>agent=cogni-ai-code-reviewer]
        CommentCheck -->|Matches TRIGGERS or BotMention| SetParsed[run=true<br/>agent=getAgent body]
        CommentCheck -->|No Match| Skip[run=false]

        PRCheck -->|Allowed Role / Copilot Login| SetDefaultPR[run=true<br/>agent=cogni-ai-architect]
        PRCheck -->|Not Allowed| Skip

        SetDefault --> FinalAgent[Output: run & effective_agent]
        SetReviewer --> FinalAgent
        SetParsed --> FinalAgent
        SetDefaultPR --> FinalAgent
        Skip --> FinalAgent
    end

    FinalAgent --> ShouldRun{run == 'true'?}
    ShouldRun -->|No| EndSkipped([End - Action Skipped])
    ShouldRun -->|Yes| WaitConcurrency

    subgraph Step 2: Wait for concurrent runs
        WaitConcurrency[Poll for older runs]
        WaitConcurrency --> |Older active runs found| Delay[Wait 30s]
        Delay --> WaitConcurrency
        WaitConcurrency --> |No older runs or Timeout 20m| ResolvePrompt[Resolve prompt]
    end

    subgraph Step 3: Prepare Environment
        ResolvePrompt --> |Builds Prompt text<br/>adds Re-run notes| Checkout[Clone Dependencies]
        Checkout --> |Checkout cogni-ai-agents / instructions / skills| permissions[Convert permissions to JSON]
        permissions --> |Merges default & agent perms| opencode[Run opencode]
    end

    subgraph Step 4: Agent Execution
        opencode -->|Executes configured agent| EvaluateResult
    end

    subgraph Step 5: Post-Run
        EvaluateResult{Response exists?}
        EvaluateResult -->|Yes| WriteSummary[Write response to summary]
        EvaluateResult -->|No| CheckFailure
        WriteSummary --> CheckFailure

        CheckFailure{Job Failed or Cancelled?}
        CheckFailure -->|Yes| PrintLogs[Print logs]
        CheckFailure -->|No| End([End])
        PrintLogs --> End
    end
